  ((SELECT id FROM mock_test_bank WHERE exam_type = 'TOPIK_II' AND test_number = 83 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1), 'reading', 14, '다음을 순서에 맞게 배열한 것을 고르십시오.

